OL,3,CMan dies after motorway lorry crash
OL,5,FA 48-year-old man has died after being
OL,6,Fhit by a lorry on the M57.
OL,8,FThe incident happened Northbound
OL,9,Fbetween junction two and three just
OL,10,Fbefore 3.45am on Saturday 20 April.
OL,12,FThe man was sadly pronounced dead at
OL,13,Fthe scene and is yet to be formally
OL,14,Fidentified.
