OL,3,CMan dies after motorway lorry crash
OL,5,FHis next of kin have been informed and
OL,6,Fare being supported by specially
OL,7,Ftrained officers.JThe lorry driver
OL,8,Fstopped at the scene and assisted
OL,9,Fpolice with their enquiries.JOfficers
OL,10,Ffrom Merseyside Police Roads Policing
OL,11,FUnit and the North West Motorway
OL,12,FPolice Group remain at scene and a
OL,13,Fpolice investigation is ongoing in the
OL,14,Farea.
