OL,3,CMan dies after motorway lorry crash
OL,5,FDue to the nature of the incident,
OL,6,Fboth Northbound and Southbound
OL,7,Fcarriageways have been fully closed
OL,8,Fand diversions are in place.JDetective
OL,9,FSergeant Kurt Timpson, Lead
OL,10,FInvestigating Officer from the
OL,11,FMerseyside Police Serious Collision
OL,12,FInvestigation Unit said: "My thoughts
OL,13,Fare with the man's family at this sad
OL,14,Ftime. They are being supported by
OL,15,Fspecially trained Police Officers.
