OL,5,F"An investigation is now taking place
OL,6,Fand it is important that Officers have
OL,7,Fthe time and safe space to complete
OL,8,Fthese enquiries.J"I am aware that the
OL,9,Fclosure of this main road network will
OL,10,Fcause issues for motorists and would
OL,11,Fencourage you to avoid the area and
OL,12,Fuse alternative routes. The Motorway
OL,13,Fis likely to remain closed for many
OL,14,Fhours, but we will work to re-open it
OL,15,Fas soon as we can.J"I would like to
OL,16,Fappeal to anyone who was on the M57 at
OL,17,Fthe time of this collision to please
OL,18,Fget in touch. We know from initial
OL,19,Fenquiries that several other vehicles
OL,20,Fpassed through this area just prior or
OL,21,Fjust after the collision. The vehicle
OL,22,Finvolved was a DAF Heavy Goods Vehicle
OL,23,Fand the collision happened at 3.40am
OL,24,Fthis morning.J"Any information you can
OL,25,Fgive us may help us to get answers for
OL,26,Fhis family. Please can motorists check
OL,26,@pD@ROUwD@TOU@E@OOUGE@dO]
